## Execution Order

1. **Storage Foundation** — everything depends on it
2. **Telegram Client** — infrastructure needed by refresh and cmd
3. **Source System** — content abstraction needed by refresh and summarizer
4. **Refresh Pipeline** — bridges telegram + source into storage
5. **Summarizer** — depends on storage + source
6. **TUI** — UI layer, depends on storage + cmd adapters
7. **CLI Orchestrator** — wiring layer, run last when all boundaries are mapped

Total: 34 production files covered across 7 slices (53 total files minus 19 test files = 34).
